*"Ona prodaje slatkiše." (She sells candy.) 
*"Šta prodaješ?" (What are you selling?) 
*"Oni prodaju svoje stvari na pijaci." (They are selling their things at the market.) 
*"Šta prodajemo?" (What are we selling?) 
*"Oni prodaju nove proizvode." (They are selling new products.) 
*"Gde se prodaju obuća?" (Where are shoes sold?) 
*"Oni prodaju svoje proizvode preko interneta." (They are selling their products online.) 
*"Ko prodaje ovo?" (Who is selling this?)